From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Fri, 24 Apr 2026 22:57:03 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] feat: landing page, full bug fixes, Gemini AI, new pages
 (reports/suppliers/help)
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- index.html: complete marketing landing page (hero, features, pricing, CTA, login modal)
- login.html: standalone login/register page
- auth.js: added openModal/closeModal globals, fixed requireAuth redirect to /login.html
- sidebar.js: dynamically builds sidebar HTML if missing (fixes compta/all pages)
- api.js: invoice PDF download via fetch+Blob with Bearer token (was broken link)
- dashboard.html/js: KPI cards, Chart.js revenue & source charts, recent orders table
- compta.html/js: fixed auth key (ecom_user), table id, search, CSV export with BOM
- ads.html/js: fixed adTitle→adName mismatch, Chart.js charts, full CRUD
- ugc.html/js: fixed canvas (div→real <canvas> injected by JS), templates system
- reports.html/js: full reports page, client-side PDF (print) & CSV download
- suppliers.html/js: full CRUD suppliers with localStorage, filters, CSV export
- help.html: FAQ accordion, Gemini API key configuration, contact section
- gemini.js: Gemini 1.5 Flash integration for AI assistant (chat.html, bot.html)
- vercel.json: fixed outputDirectory, explicit routes for all pages

